-- Mizuho Securities and Shinko Sec to merge, sources say
-- 
-- Tue Jan 9, 2007 7:44pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/10/businesspro-mizuho-shinko-merger-dc-idUSTKU00275520070110

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Brokerages Mizuho Securities Co. and 
Shinko Securities Co. 8606.T, both affiliated with Mizuho 
Financial Group Inc. ( 8411.T ), have agreed to merge around 
January 2008, sources close to the matter said on Wednesday. 

  The two companies will announce the deal as early as this 
afternoon, they said.